column1: # Supplementary Data 1 for Lovell et al. 'The genomic landscape of molecular responses to natural drought stress in Panicum hallii'.

# Description: Here, we present library sequencing identifiers, public repository information and sequencing effort data for each of the re-sequenced genotypes used in the population genetic analysis.
## Library_Name: a unique identifier for the library for internal use by the JGI
## BioProject: NCBI bioproject identifier. Searchable at https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/bioproject/.
## BioSample: NCBI biosample identifier. Searchable at https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/biosample
## Experiment: NCBI experiment identifier. Searchable at https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sra
## Mbases: number of nucleotides sequences in millions (Mb).
## Mbytes: amount of data sequences in Mb.
## SRA_sample: SRA bioproject identifier. Searchable at https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sra
## SRA_study: SRA study identifier. Searchable at https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sra
## Sample_Name: Phytozome sample identifier. Searchable at https://genome.jgi.doe.gov/portal/Panhalsequencing_54/
## Variety: Variety name of the sample
## sample ID: The Juenger lab unique identifier of the sample
